name: Sembwaste
description: SembWaste is the largest municipal waste collection company in Singapore, serving 5,000 industrial and commercial, government agencies and healthcare establishments daily and over 600,000 households, schools and trade premises. They provide Collection and Post-collection Treatment for General Waste and Recyclables. Sembcorp also operates a Waste-To-Energy plant to supply steam for the local industries in Jurong Island, Singapore.
